{"tid":201393,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺有時個天好似阻住你，令你得唔到你想要嘅嘢？","createTime":"2017-04-14T16:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T17:34:20.000Z","uid":6841,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8d8b8d57e164c38d49245a5cf60d7260b440d65e","tid":201393,"uid":6841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T16:58:54.000Z","msg":"有時我會覺得命運總係會阻礙你，令你得唔到想要嘅嘢咁。無論你幾努力都好，你都好難得到嗰樣嘢（感情除外）<br />\n我係講緊死物<br />\n例如：學位、金錢、樓、車<br />\n我努力咗好耐，堅持咗好耐，但係都得唔到我想要嘅嘢<br />\n係咪一得到我就會死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解上天要阻止我？<br />\n好似學跳舞咁，每次練舞都會發生意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係行街仆親就係扭親。搞到學唔成，連續幾年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係我想放棄，係個天放棄我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身我係一個又毒又矮嘅肥仔，的起心肝想去跑步減肥<br />\n但次次中途都會受傷，之後又要養傷，結果又係肥返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟我點解我咁黑仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知有冇人有咁嘅經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能我講到1999咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d8cb74e19f31c10f3462c0be8f975810494fbc7","tid":201393,"uid":72186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:16:05.000Z","msg":"當面對住個天屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同佢講咪阻撚住晒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後就繼續努力 你終會有日成功嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做事成功唔係上天開綠燈比你 係靠自己㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c299cd8dd64a22f1b796e3b62be66060caa5f47","tid":201393,"uid":79735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:20:27.000Z","msg":"努力嘅路就好似行緊上坡路咁<br />\n你逾行就只會逾辛苦逾多阻滯<br />\n咁只係證明你真係努力緊<br />\n所以巴打加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b66665bc3285e2552471956feedf1e4f1c01bceb","tid":201393,"uid":6841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:33:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當面對住個天屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同佢講咪阻撚住晒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後就繼續努力 你終會有日成功嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做事成功唔係上天開綠燈比你 係靠自己㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好有呢種感覺<br />\n特別係早兩日考完數學我行出考場都好想大叫屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6160408324a053f0c3f248714264471491ec17f4","tid":201393,"uid":6841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:34:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>努力嘅路就好似行緊上坡路咁<br />\n你逾行就只會逾辛苦逾多阻滯<br />\n咁只係證明你真係努力緊<br />\n所以巴打加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}